						<p>Much damaged. Seems to contain a verse in praise of king <hi rend="bold">Mīṉavaṉ</hi> (evidently <hi rend="bold">Jaṭāvarmaṉ Sundara-Pāṇḍya</hi>). A section of the record however, mentions the name <hi rend="bold">Poṉmēynda-Perumāḷ-dāsaṉ</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Pārthasārathi</hi> (See No. 197 above). Engraved in characters of <hi rend="bold">13th century A.D.</hi></p>						

